-- Index the unindexed foreign-key columns + the incidents dashboard filter columns.
-- 103 declared FK columns had no leading index (RI cascades + joins were full scans); the response
-- dashboard filters/sorts incidents by status + reported_at unindexed. All additive + idempotent.
-- NOTE: created non-CONCURRENTLY (Flyway runs migrations in a transaction); on a large production
-- table a DBA may prefer CREATE INDEX CONCURRENTLY out-of-band. On dev volumes this is instant.

-- ── Foreign-key columns (generated from pg_constraint: every FK whose leading column lacked an index) ──
